        "Params": "{3: 'The edge of the sky fades from the brilliance of daylight to a bright blue when the transport craft crosses the atmospheric boundary. In the direction from which the sunlight beams, the gem-like colors gradually spread to the horizon.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 4,
