        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Having been given a piece of mind by Qu, you turn to focus on piloting the aircraft.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 80,
        "ActionId": 81,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Save for the engine\\'s roar, the cabin has fallen completely quiet.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 81,
        "ActionId": 82,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Qu crosses her legs casually, gazing at you as if she has something to say.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 82,
        "ActionId": 83,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But when you meet her gaze, she turns her head toward the porthole and starts admiring the view outside.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 83,
        "ActionId": 84,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'This goes on a few more times, until Qu gets tired of this little hide-and-seek and decides to face you.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 84,
        "ActionId": 85,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500817'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 85,
        "ActionId": 86,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Qu', 3: 'I didn\\'t come just to have a date with you.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 86,
        "ActionId": 87,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Want to know what else I came to do?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 87,
        "ActionId": 88,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Sure.', 3: '89', 4: 'I don\\'t much care.', 5: '90'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 88,
        "ActionId": 89,
        "NextActionId": 92,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Well, here is why.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 89,
        "ActionId": 90,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Is that so? But you\\'re supposed to familiarize yourself with the details of the mission you\\'re on, right?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 90,
        "ActionId": 91,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'In the interest of helping you stay on the ball, here is why.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 91,
        "ActionId": 92,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'So I got a physical letter about a month and a half ago from Babylonia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 92,
        "ActionId": 93,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'And I was a little confused at first because I didn\\'t remember writing physical letters being part of Babylonia\\'s tradition.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 93,
        "ActionId": 94,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'But things started to make sense to me when I saw the sender\\'s name.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 94,
        "ActionId": 95,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'The sender was Hengzhu, former administrator of Kowloong\\'s observatory before the Punishing struck. He was as much a loyal subordinate of mine as he was my mentor, for giving me all sorts of suggestions on building Kowloong.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 95,
        "ActionId": 96,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'I thought he\\'d died from the Punishing, but it turned out that he survived and moved to Babylonia. He works as an astronomer there now.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 96,
        "ActionId": 97,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'But something hit me when I opened the envelope feeling relief.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 97,
        "ActionId": 98,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'That Hengzhu should be quite old now in human years.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 99,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'And given that the letter came at this time, something came to my mind.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 100,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Knowing him and considering his pride, leaving Kowloong would have meant that he\\'d parted ways with his past.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'And that he\\'d never have swallowed his pride and written me this letter unless he was coming close to the end of his life.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'And it turned out I was right. The letter was a farewell letter.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'A farewell letter?', 3: '104'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'There used to be this tradition in Kowloong where people would write letters to their masters bidding farewell when they felt their days were numbered.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Hengzhu no longer lives in Kowloong, but he follows this tradition nonetheless.', 4: '1'}"
    },
